Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wit is your weapon{honestly no clue what is megurase here, deepl says "rack one's brain"}\NRemember to use your head{智恵をめぐらせ 頭を使え}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Repress your anguish, \NIf you are a man{悩み抜け抜け 男なら}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One decision is enough \NTo make others cry or laugh{泣くも笑うも 決断ひとつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, don't hold your head high, \NIf you lose, don't cry{勝っておごるな 敗れて泣くな}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, don't you ever let other see your tears{男 涙は見せぬもの}
Comment: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ch}
Comment: 0,0:24:43.11,0:24:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{ch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a man, let's put your strength to test{男だったら　力を試せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a man, keep your hopes sizzling{男だったら　希望(のぞみ)を燃やせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a man, don't lose your heart{男だったら　くじけるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:25:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's just you and me, a man and a man{俺もおまえも　男と男}
